  "remarks": "Na Man was listed on 18 Jul. 2012 pursuant to paragraph 4 of resolution 2048 (2012) as “Member of the “Military Command” which has assumed responsibility for the coup d'état of 12 April 2012. Also a member of the Military High Command (highest hierarchy of the Bissau-Guinean Armed Forces).” Father’s name is Biute Naman; Mother’s name is Ndjade Na Noa. INTERPOL-UN Security Council Special Notice web link: https://www.interpol.int/en/notice/search/un/5782448",
